<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>HOME</title>

    <!-- style css -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/css/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/css/nav.css" />

    <!-- script font awesome -->
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/b9d0ad08e2.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav>
      <div class="left">
        <ul>
          <img src="../assets/image/logo.png" alt="logo" />
          <li class="active">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/add-blog">Add Project</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/testimonial">Testimonial</a>
          </li>
          <div class="log">
            {{#if isLogin}}
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link fw-bold active text-danger">Hello,
                  {{users}}</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item ms-3">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
              </li>
            {{else}}
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item ms-3">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
              </li>
            {{/if}}
          </div>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-end">
        <div class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 ms-5 mb-lg-0">
          <div class="hamberger">
            <button onclick="openHamberger()">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-bars fa-2xl"></i>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
          <a class="btn btn-danger btn-submit ms-5" href="/contact-me">Contact
            Me</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    {{#if messages.succes}}
      <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
        <div class="container">
          {{messages.succes}}
        </div>
      </div>
    {{/if}}

    <div class="hamberger-bars-items" id="hamberger-bars-items">
      <a href="/" class="active">Home</a>
      <a href="/add-blog">Add Project</a>
      <a href="/testimonial">Testimonial</a>
      {{#if isLogin}}
        <a class="nav-item nav-link fw-bold active text-danger">Hello,
          {{users}}</a>
        <a class="nav-item ms-3 nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
      {{else}}
        <a class="nav-item nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
        <a class="nav-item ms-3 nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
      {{/if}}
      <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="content_card">
          <h2>Hi Welcome to my Profil</h2>
          <p class="content_msg">
            Halo semua, saya Ikhsan Taufik, dan saya sangat senang dapat berbagi
            sedikit tentang diri saya. Saya memiliki keahlian khusus dalam Web
            Development dan telah sedang berlatih dalam pelatihan bootcamp
            Dumbways. Sebagai seorang Pekerja, saya selalu berusaha untuk
            meningkatkan diri saya dan mencari peluang baru untuk berkembang.
            Saya percaya pada kolaborasi dan tim, dan saya senang bekerja dengan
            orang-orang yang memiliki visi dan semangat yang sama. Terima kasih
            telah mengambil waktu untuk membaca sedikit tentang saya. Saya
            sangat bersemangat untuk dapat dinamis, seperti Dumbways ini.
            berkontribusi dan belajar lebih lanjut di lingkungan yang positif
            dan.
          </p>

          <div class="content_btn">
            <button><a href="/contact.html">contact</a></button>
            <p>
              <a
                href="https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1FsRxvpIAzpt3JxvGzcZX24bjuPtR3BOP&amp;export=download&amp;authuser=0&amp;confirm=t&amp;uuid=a812aa28-7c8e-4ca9-8cb7-bf0062aa0ac5&amp;at=APZUnTXlrYc5dSXKqEje5SmqarNI:1707725703411"
                download
              >download CV
                <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i>
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="content_socialmedia">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ikhsan-psd-2a490922a/">
              <img src="../assets/image/icons/linkedin.png" alt="linkedin" />
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/ikhsan_ta/">
              <img src="../assets/image/icons/instagram.png" alt="instagram" />
            </a>
            <a href="https://id-id.facebook.com">
              <img src="../assets/image/icons/facebook.png" alt="facebook" />
            </a>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/ikhsan78461">
              <img src="../assets/image/icons/twitter.png" alt="twitter" />
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="profile">
        <div class="profile_card">
          <img src="../assets/image/person.jpg" alt="person" />
          <h2>Ikhsan Taufik</h2>
          <p>Fullstack Developer</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PROJECT LIST -->
    <div class="container-project-list">
      <div class="container-blog">
        <h1>MY PROJECT</h1>
        <div class="blog-card" id="blog-card">
          {{#each data}}
            <div class="card">
              <a href="./blog-details.html?id=${index}">
                <img
                  src="uploads/{{this.image}}"
                  class="img-fluid"
                  alt="image-review"
                />

                <p class="card-title">
                  <a
                    href="/add-blog/{{this.id}}"
                    target="_blank"
                  >{{this.title}}</a></p>
                <p class="card-duration">date :
                  {{this.updatedAt}}
                  |
                  {{this.author}}</p>
                <div class="card-content">
                  <p>{{this.description}}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-icon">
                  {{#if this.reactjs}}
                    <i class="mt-5 me-2"><i class="fa-brands fa-react"></i></i>
                  {{/if}}
                  {{#if this.nodejs}}
                    <i class="mt-5 me-2"><i
                        class="fa-brands fa-node-js"
                      ></i></i>
                  {{/if}}
                  {{#if this.java}}
                    <i class="mt-5 me-2"><i class="fa-brands fa-java"></i></i>
                  {{/if}}
                  {{#if this.javascript}}
                    <i class="mt-5 me-2"><i class="fa-brands fa-js"></i></i>
                  {{/if}}</div>
              </a>
              <div class="card-btn">
                {{#if this.isLogin}}
                  <div class="d-flex justify-content-end">
                    <a
                      href="/edit-blog/{{this.id}}"
                      class="btn btn-secondary text-decoration-none me-3 px-3 py-1"
                      style="font-size: 14px;"
                    >EDIT</a>
                    <a
                      href="/delete-blog/{{this.id}}"
                      class="btn btn-danger text-decoration-none px-3 py-1"
                      style="font-size: 14px;"
                    >DELETE</a>
                  </div>
                {{/if}}
              </div>
            </div>
          {{/each}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
  <script src="../assets/js/blog.js"></script>
  <script src="../assets/js/nav.js"></script>
</html>